    <h1>Nueva Vizcaya Provincial Museum - ARTMO</h1>
    <p class="lead">Artmo brings an Augmented Reality Technology to Nueva Vizcaya Provincial Museum.</p>
    <hr />
    <br />
    <p>Experience Augmented Reality  by downloading ARTMO and by visiting Nueva Vizcaya People's Library and Museum.</p>
    @Html.ActionLink("Download Artmo", "Download", "Artmo", null, new { @class = "btn btn-dark btn-lg ripple", title = "Download Artmo" })
    <hr class="my-4">
    <p>
        ARTMO is a ANDROID Mobile Application  using Augmented Reality(AR) Technology to offer an innovative experience of showcasing Nueva Vizcaya's historical and cultural artifacts. It gives a superimposed reality that enhaces your perception of reality through 3D objects on the screen by scanning Target Images which can only be available at the Museum. It provides the different information and details of the different artifacts such as native names, english terms, descriptions and more! You can also learn more through watching videos or listen to sounds.
    </p>
    <p>
        If you are not fond of reading, you can also choose to listen to a narration audio while looking at the artifacts in more detail. It also gives a cultural touch by giving you an option of choosing Ilocano as the application's language.
    </p>
