                <div class="card-body">
                    The "ART-" in ARTMO is possibly an abbreviation from the words ART-ifact and A-ugmented R-eality T-echnology which gives a 2-in-1 meaning, while the "-MO" is abbreviated from MO-bile application. Combined the two, it forms ARTMO.
