                    <button class="btn btn-link collapsed text-black" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSeven">
                        WHAT TO DO IF MY DEVICE CANNOT INSTALL THE APPLICATION?
                    </button>
                </h5>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseSeven" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSeven" data-parent="#accordionParent">
                <div class="card-body">
                    1.) Check your device storage<br />
                    Your device must have atleast free 300 MB of storage in order to install the application<br />
                    2.) Check your settings<br />
                    Go to your device settings and navigate to your Application Settings >> Check "Unknown Sources" (Allows installation of non-market applications).<br />
                    3.) Ask for assistance<br />
                    <b>Ask for the museum staff for any more encountered problems</b>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
